Package: scGPS
Type: Package
Title: An implementation of clustering and subpopulation relationship analysis (scGPS = single cell Global Predictions of Subpopulation)
Version: 0.9.9
Authors@R: c(
    person("Quan", "Nguyen", email="quan.nguyen@uq.edu.au", role=c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Anne", "Asenbouth",role=c("aut"))
    )
Description: The package implements two main algorithms to answer two key questions: a CORE (Clustering at Optimal REsolution) to find subpopulations, followed by scGPS to investigate the relationships between subpopulations. A compatible software that can run CORE is ascend R package.
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
License: GPL-3
BugReports:  https://github.com/IMB-Computational-Genomics-Lab/scGPS/issues
url:  https://github.com/IMB-Computational-Genomics-Lab/scGPS/
